<li>Food Vendors (Warner School Parking Lot): 5 PM – 9PM</li>
<li>Pub Crawl Begins at 5:30 PM at New Boswell Brewery and end at the Ice Fights at 7:30 PM.  5:30 PM – 7 PM</li>
<li>Cork and Canvas: 6 PM– 9 PM  (Must register to attend at <a href="http://richmondartmuseum.org/" target="_blank">RichmondArtMuseum.org</a>  $35/person)</li>
