</ul>
<h3>Saturday, January 30 Richmond Meltdown Events</h3>
<p>Warming Stations open 12 PM – 6 PM at: Roscoe’s Coffee Bar and Tap Room and Joe’s Pizza. Free activities provided.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/452564421616892/" target="_blank">Ice Carving in the Work Zone</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/885124131605148/" target="_blank">Family Fun Zone</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/207894009553508/" target="_blank">Freeze Your Buns Off – Fun Run</a>:  7:30 AM Meet in the 6th Street Parking Lot.  Free!</li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1686451708239416/" target="_blank">Frozen Fairy Trail</a>: 10 AM – 4 PM Begins at Old National Road Welcome Center, 5701 National Road East, and includes ten other stops.</li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1090092464347763/" target="_blank">Paint and Take Souvenirs:</a> 10 AM – 7 PM</li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/157050657999400/permalink/157050667999399/" target="_blank">Veach’s Family Game Day</a>: 10 AM– 5 PM</li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1705872919658694/" target="_blank">Warm up at Grassroots Center</a>: 10 AM– 6 PM<a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1705872919658694/" target="_blank"> </a></li>
<li>Treasure Hunt</li>
