<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/1704363129809662/" target="_blank">Main Event: ICE FIGHTS</a>: 7:30 PM</li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/460366410819642/" target="_blank">Art Show Opening Reception</a>: 9 PM – 11 PM</li>
</ul>
<p>How long will the ice sculptures remain around downtown Richmond? Let&#8217;s just say it&#8217;s &#8220;<strong>weather permitting</strong>.&#8221;</p>
<p>To learn more, <strong>check out <a href="http://www.richmondmeltdown.com/" target="_blank">Richmond Meltdown</a> </strong>and follow in the fun on the <strong><a href="https://www.facebook.com/RichmondMeltdown/" target="_blank">Richmond Meltdown Facebook Page</a></strong>. Bonus: why not start a hashtag trend? Share #RichmondMeltdown across your social networks so everyone can join in the fun!</p>
