<h3><strong>Yoga in Brown County</strong></h3>
<figure id="attachment_53521" style="width: 600px;" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://littleindiana.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Winter-in-the-Woods-Brown-County-Indiana.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-53521" src="http://littleindiana.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Winter-in-the-Woods-Brown-County-Indiana.jpg" alt="Winter in the Woods in Brown County, Indiana Shows There's More to Brown County than Autumn Leaves!" width="600" height="380" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Winter in the Woods in Brown County, Indiana Shows There&#8217;s More to Brown County than Autumn Leaves!</figcaption></figure>
Take time out for you for a change.<strong> See why yoga has been a beneficial practice for 5,000 years</strong>. As Lee mentions on her website, &#8221; Restorative yoga and meditation particularly have been linked with improvements in cardiovascular health and stress-related disease.&#8221; Let your journey begin with people who know in a place that understands.</p>
<p>As Lee also stated on her site, &#8220;The promises of yoga are extensive: <strong>physical health and beauty, spiritual expression, and social connection</strong>.&#8221; At the Winter in the Woods retreat, you can easily attain all three.</p>
<p>For course information and instructor details, look to EventBrite to <strong><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/warm-up-from-within-the-fifth-unfolding-tickets-19412040937?ref=enivtefor001&amp;invite=ODcxNDE5Mi9qZWxsaXNAYnJvd25jb3VudHkuY29tLzA%3D&amp;utm_source=eb_email&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=inviteformalv2&amp;ref=enivtefor001&amp;utm_term=attend" target="_blank">buy your Warm Up from Within tickets</a> for January 15-17, 2016.</strong> The rest of the Winter in the Woods Events feature separate admissions. See the appropriate links in the article for purchase information.</p>
<h3><strong>Wrap it Up on Sunday with Trail Hobo</strong></h3>
<p>It&#8217;s dutch oven meal time fun for the <strong><a href="http://www.browncounty.com/calendar/event/trail-cache--dutch-oven-cookout-1" target="_blank">Trail Cache and Dutch Oven Cookout</a></strong>. Trail Hobo will be cooking up a hearty meal, just like the pioneers. But before you dig in, there&#8217;s geocaching to do! Make sure you have the app installed on your smartphone and know how to use it (trust me, it&#8217;s so easy) before you participate with your $5 event fee.</p>
<p><strong>Be sure to <a href="http://www.facebook.com/events/1669885609953742/" target="_blank">RSVP on the Trail Cache and Dutch Oven Cookout Facebook Page</a> so they have enough prepared for everyone</strong>!</p>
<p>Keep those New Year Resolutions for the first time, um, ever with a visit to<strong> Winter in the Woods in Brown County</strong>. It promises to be a lovely new way to ring in the new year&#8211;while getting (or staying) in shape.</p>
